"uid":56051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T21:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一次去 有啲淆底</blockquote><br />\n咩城市</blockquote><br />\n先去幾日london</blockquote><br />\n倫敦可以叫全歐洲其中一個最安全城市，相對法國德國果啲，算搗破左好多單恐襲<br />\n<br />\n雖然黑人區日日都有人淋漒水攞刀仔拮人，你係遊客基本上唔會去果啲地方<br />\n<br />\n最大危機係人多地方俾人打荷包，偷電話<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，講治安香港真係世界上最好果堆，好少大城市係治安好"},{"pid":"d7c81c33f7efe6372c1f7705f3365ee1a0802585","tid":248760,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T21:48:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8712ecdd84035bee03d3d682763b0aac13e831f","tid":248760,"uid":71227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T21:51:11.000Z","msg":"人在liverpool<br />\n小心 佢地對亞洲人好偏見<br />\n小心紅藍色衫盡避免"},{"pid":"1d278055d75478cae8ac916744a5feb836363fcc","tid":248760,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:02:15.000Z","msg":"英格蘭愈北愈雜，Manchester 小心財物"},{"pid":"bf770aa5d4f4ddfd9f0010259127c9d6be754cfb","tid":248760,"uid":46631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:11:45.000Z","msg":"雖然好安全，啲人好有禮貌，<br />\n但都要小心。<br />\n如果有古怪既陌生人搭爹或露宿者問你拎錢，同佢講Sorry就走得。"},{"pid":"70b031eb3e47ff50208fb4c8935d3efbe5ce078a","tid":248760,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:46:28.000Z","msg":"驚乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住倫敦 治安幾好<br />\n我一個女仔成日自己周圍行都無事<br />\n自己一個坐火車周圍去都無問題<br />\n唔知你驚乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532f22f9b28b027de787ec58469181fd747ea28f","tid":248760,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>London都安全，但千祈唔好一路行一路按電話，尤其iPhone,之前有兩個女仔friend 俾人當街搶iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我成日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9937e0d403489046b157433b04f019f6f15520","tid":248760,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T22:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人在liverpool<br />\n小心 佢地對亞洲人好偏見<br />\n小心紅藍色衫盡避免</blockquote><br />\n點解紅藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196fcfafa38411fc6893b29287e7abcbaf3676c3","tid":248760,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人在liverpool<br />\n小心 佢地對亞洲人好偏見<br />\n小心紅藍色衫盡避免</blockquote><br />\n點解紅藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利物浦/愛華頓"},{"pid":"5e0566f4de6f560df0a6679e9b83ae2f50bcf015","tid":248760,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人在liverpool<br />\n小心 佢地對亞洲人好偏見<br />\n小心紅藍色衫盡避免</blockquote><br />\n點解紅藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利物浦/愛華頓</blockquote><br />\n呀係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661680a28568cebca6fa5d4f613eb30f143c6d1b","tid":248760,"uid":91899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"e2e6345182a8628cde532c18643b536c16f36b44","tid":248760,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:39:56.000Z","msg":"好危險，恐怖襲擊機會好高"},{"pid":"bc7ab1f2aa1a7e2ee8d4754f0f9df75449f4a0bf","tid":248760,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:40:24.000Z","msg":"Knife crime 極高，無啦啦用刀插人"},{"pid":"24806133d009bd4cc4e7b683a52eb0d680c6858d","tid":248760,"uid":109513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:48:59.000Z","msg":"太夜就唔好單獨出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友係屋企附近比人搶電腦比人抽水，有個就比班人打，去咗醫院聯咗幾針"},{"pid":"6cde90a0a2ec377a539c5437c347ff7e0db8411b","tid":248760,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T00:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太夜就唔好單獨出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友係屋企附近比人搶電腦比人抽水，有個就比班人打，去咗醫院聯咗幾針</blockquote><br />\nZone幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea71aba9253565c8de830ff59e553961a0f24d2","tid":248760,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:20:05.000Z","msg":"倫敦無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bf25842533a74bd46084c3e3fcc7992937ca39","tid":248760,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英格蘭愈北愈雜，Manchester 小心財物</blockquote><br />\n早幾個月去又冇咩野 感覺上治安幾好"},{"pid":"a4b1fd93ee27a430158941675dd4ebf241c49be7","tid":248760,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"倫敦嘅話基本上冇乜嘢嘅<br />\n但小心財物啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住香港咁大安旨意<br />\n等車搭車嗰啲有時會有人撩你借錢搭車之類嘅，但你唔理佢或者say no嘅話就自動走人<br />\n<br />\n其實一般旅客通常留喺zone one，最多係去Wimbledon/Kew Gardens/Greenwich <br />\n呢啲地方都唔算話有咩大問題嘅"},{"pid":"e758c7dc6a6e43930f5504f13fed4a1e3cd8e5b7","tid":248760,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔入黑鬼竇就無問題</blockquote><br />\n咩地方多黑鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一向印象<br />\n西邊有錢，東邊窮<br />\n南面 Brixton (zone 2)就出咗名比較多黑鬼<br />\n東面一過咗Aldgate就係阿差聚集地，過咗Stratford加個更字，招牌都多咗印度文/阿拉伯文<br />\nHolloway/Finsbury Park 嗰邊都多少少阿差，但主要聚喺大街，離開咗大街就冇咁明顯<br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲地方你唔係屎忽痕（好似我咁）都唔會特登走過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6df6a0ff7588993881c130b64e34779a31e734","tid":248760,"uid":59509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"新手都係留番係Chinatown算啦"},{"pid":"d587e910c8d525ef3fa12a30581d8ca1bf7f0d7f","tid":248760,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:53:04.000Z","msg":"倫敦會有啲扮電影角色嘅鳩人埋嚟叫你影相<br />\n之後就問你拎錢<br />\n嚟唔好理佢哋就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bac909cc944a4edb9a14eaf199e65ce922f7bf0","tid":248760,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔入黑鬼竇就無問題</blockquote><br />\n咩地方多黑鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一向印象<br />\n西邊有錢，東邊窮<br />\n南面 Brixton (zone 2)就出咗名比較多黑鬼<br />\n東面一過咗Aldgate就係阿差聚集地，過咗Stratford加個更字，招牌都多咗印度文/阿拉伯文<br />\nHolloway/Finsbury Park 嗰邊都多少少阿差，但主要聚喺大街，離開咗大街就冇咁明顯<br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲地方你唔係屎忽痕（好似我咁）都唔會特登走過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nStratford我行完個商場就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320fcfaa44ce595a46110bfc5e30caa2c1b35dca","tid":248760,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"PLAN左住5日ZONE3<br />\nACTON區<br />\n有無問題?"},{"pid":"ee94a9c53f65b9757741ed476eeeb19b42372d61","tid":248760,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PLAN左住5日ZONE3<br />\nACTON區<br />\n有無問題?</blockquote><br />\nrip"},{"pid":"3047e2dc74eb803d41fc2f3af6fc1b44e4abc22e","tid":248760,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lon