85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:26:51.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪去summer exchange?"},{"pid":"7517fc8b00f49677ff1fbf5d178448c6c165b9c0","tid":248760,"uid":356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:29:01.000Z","msg":"好安全我覺得<br />\n你正常自己睇好自己啲野就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日仲覺得有啲危險<br />\n之後一路行一路用電話都無乜問題"},{"pid":"b472f40b68d557ba2dec0385e94205323d23126e","tid":248760,"uid":8579,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Edinburgh 食飯好貴</blockquote><br />\n你去完倫敦再下結論啦"},{"pid":"14caa7e92061777d568d91de7ec303bdbde8b542","tid":248760,"uid":26361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:35:18.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺倫敦走 好安全<br />\n依加喺Frankfurt 先驚"},{"pid":"a5b58ae909728dc42180facba4c1aa1ba8254b36","tid":248760,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:38:57.000Z","msg":"獌係痴撚線<br />\n記得舊年去summer school<br />\n係曼機場坐尾班鐵番york<br />\n曼個站成班醉酒癲佬上曬車<br />\n去到列斯先落<br />\n成程好似ocamp dem beat咁癲撚左<br />\n但其實冇乜野<br />\n<br />\n一句，醉酒佬你千奇咪撚搞<br />\n佢地飲醉乜鳩都有<br />\n利同曼好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曼街頭好撚多人聊鳩你問你拎錢<br />\n唔洗理佢 行開就得<br />\n<br />\n倫敦住個wembley果頭係安全<br />\n一區遊客區實冇事<br />\n但東面就唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf9633d9fbd99ba0cee1640208a3fbd66df012d","tid":248760,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:42:31.000Z","msg":"住過Brixton 九點後醉酒啪藥既出哂黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n北面好好撚多啲人有錢啲成個neighborhood 都唔同啲<br />\n<br />\n如果驚既啲local 教搭巴士唔好上上層 <br />\n<br />\n好多年前既事 而家係點就唔知道啦"},{"pid":"1b6293773ac7a80284879db9f310c0480aff7af4","tid":248760,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一次去 有啲淆底</blockquote><br />\n咩城市</blockquote><br />\n先去幾日london</blockquote><br />\n倫敦可以叫全歐洲其中一個最安全城市，相對法國德國果啲，算搗破左好多單恐襲<br />\n<br />\n雖然黑人區日日都有人淋漒水攞刀仔拮人，你係遊客基本上唔會去果啲地方<br />\n<br />\n最大危機係人多地方俾人打荷包，偷電話<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，講治安香港真係世界上最好果堆，好少大城市係治安好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最安全城市？問過北歐未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倫敦咁多罪案都叫安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428160a5912f1b362a1aca8c8280a8da84ec9e74","tid":248760,"uid":48559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PLAN左住5日ZONE3<br />\nACTON區<br />\n有無問題?</blockquote><br />\n以前住Northfields ，成日會坐巴士由zone1果邊返去，會經Acton 其實我覺得冇咩野既 係多d阿拉伯人姐"},{"pid":"9719017c8c8cbdb12e0ca78433d5abbd64c5e153","tid":248760,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T22:01:14.000Z","msg":"住左兩年manchester 除左成日有人叫你比錢都無乜野"},{"pid":"e2c56a50ecb756f797c754e78bf4e598c31090e6","tid":248760,"uid":26361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T22:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱喺倫敦走 好安全<br />\n依加喺Frankfurt 先驚</blockquote><br />\nbtw 我係住west ham <br />\nstratford 隔離 都還好 我天黑前一定返去"},{"pid":"0c1e45f815dfc8cbb4d17484375362b8fa78d71a","tid":248760,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T22:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Edinburgh 食飯好貴</blockquote><br />\nGlasgow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025b60ba2cb9edab4efe540b334a3b90a14e84b8","tid":248760,"uid":17521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T22:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人在liverpool<br />\n小心 佢地對亞洲人好偏見<br />\n小心紅藍色衫盡避免</blockquote><br />\n點解紅藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利物浦/愛華頓</blockquote><br />\n原本以為係Tories 同Labour <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acadf884858308eb5a4457e873a1f6c9ee